<html>
  <head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-gH2yIJqKdNHPEq0n4Mqa/HGKIhSkIHeL5AyhkYV8i59U5AR6csBvApHHNl/vI1Bx"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-A3rJD856KowSb7dwlZdYEkO39Gagi7vIsF0jrRAoQmDKKtQBHUuLZ9AsSv4jD4Xa"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Source+Sans+Pro:wght@300;400&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <script
      src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/acfe1c41fb.js"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script
      type="text/javascript"
      src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.min.js"
    ></script>
    <style>
      :root {
        --accent-color: #e5874a;
      }
      @font-face {
        font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif, "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
        src: url("https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/projectnoonnu/noonfonts_20-04@1.0/ChosunGu.woff")
          format("woff");
        font-weight: normal;
        font-style: normal;
      }
      body {
        padding-top: 100px;
      }
      .titles {
        font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif, "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
        padding: 40px 40px 0 40px;
        color: #e5874a;
        font-size: 30px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .snack-list {
        margin: 25px;
      }
      .snack-list span {
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 8px 10px;
        color: black;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .food_name {
        display: flex;
      }
      .food_name li {
        margin-right: auto;
        margin-left: auto;
        list-style: none;
      }

      .containerbox {
        display: flex;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .image {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
      }
      .overlay {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 100%;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        background-color: #e5874a;
        overflow: hidden;
        width: 100%;
        height: 0;
        transition: 0.5s ease;
      }

      .containerbox:hover .overlay {
        bottom: 0;
        height: 100%;
      }
      .text {
        color: white;
        font-size: 20px;
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        text-align: center;
      }
      .bbq_user {
        text-align: center;
        vertical-align: middle;
      }
      .bbq_box {
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .food-kit {
        display: flex;
        margin-left: 20px;
      }

      .kit-name {
        display: none;
      }
      .kit-menu {
        display: inline-block;
        position: relative;
      }
      .kit-menu:hover:after,
      .kit-menu:hover > .kit-name {
        display: block;
      }
      .kit-menu:after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        z-index: 10;
      }
      .kit-menu {
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .kit-menu img {
        height: 270px;
      }
      .kit-menu:hover img {
        filter: blur(0.5px);
        transform: scale(1.2);
        transition: 1s;
      }
      .kit-img {
        margin: 10px;
      }
      .kit-name {
        position: absolute;
        top: 120px;
        left: 50px;
        color: #fff;
        background-color: #e5874a;
        border-radius: 10px;
        z-index: 20;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 20px;
      }
      .menu-dubu {
        left: 90px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <%-include("navbar_test.ejs")%>
    <div class="titles">밀키트</div>
    <div class="line"></div>
    <div class="food-kit row">
      <div class="kit-img col">
        <div class="kit-menu">
          <img src="/static/img/food/마파두부.jpg" alt="" />
          <p class="kit-name menu-dubu">마파두부</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="kit-img col">
        <div class="kit-menu">
          <img src="/static/img/food/나베.jpg" alt="" />
          <p class="kit-name">소고기 밀푀유 나베</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="kit-img col">
        <div class="kit-menu">
          <img src="/static/img/food/떡볶이.jpg" alt="" />
          <p class="kit-name">&nbsp;&nbsp;우삼겹 떡볶이&nbsp;</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="kit-img col">
        <div class="kit-menu">
          <img src="/static/img/food/우동전골.jpg" alt="" />
          <p class="kit-name">김치어묵 우동전골</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 class="titles">매점</h3>
    <hr />
    <div class="snack-list">
      <span>숟가락</span>
      <span>젓가락</span>
      <span>포크</span>
      <span>접시</span>
      <span>종이컵</span>
      <span>부탄가스</span>
      <span>이소가스</span>
      <span>장작</span>
      <span>라면</span>
      <span>과자</span>
      <span>쌈장</span>
      <span>햇반</span>
      <span>물</span>
      <span>커피</span>
      <span>술</span>
      <span>탄산음료</span>
      <span>얼음</span>
    </div>
    <hr />

    <div class="titles">바베큐</div>
    <div class="line"></div>
    <div class="bbq_box row">
      <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-4 containerbox">
        <div class="w-100 position-relative">
          <img src="/static/img/food/bbq.jpg" class="image" />
          <div class="overlay">
            <div class="text">
              BBQ SET <br /><br />삼겹살 500g <br />목살 500g <br />소시지
              <br />쌈set <br />쌈장 <br />새송이버섯 <br />김치
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-4 containerbox">
        <div class="w-100 position-relative">
          <img src="/static/img/food/fire.jpg" class="image" />
          <div class="overlay">
            <div class="text">
              FIRE SET <br /><br />화롯대 <br />집게 <br />숯 <br />or
              <br />장작(1회)
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bbq_user col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <div>바베큐set 미리 예약해주셔야 사용 가능합니다.</div>
        <div>자연의 경치를 바라보며 좋은 시간 보내시길 바랍니다.</div>
        <div>바베큐 set : 50,000원 (인원수상관없이) / 현장결제</div>
        <div>파이어 set : 20,000원 (인원수상관없이) / 현장결제</div>
        <div>매너시간 : 23:00시 까지</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%-include("footer.ejs")%>
  </body>
</html>
